    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/03ecfce2e82da522780ce0737c0422af.poster.avif?t=1758112013\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/03ecfce2e82da522780ce0737c0422af.webm?t=1758112013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/03ecfce2e82da522780ce0737c0422af.mp4?t=1758112013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于</h2><br>想要成为一名真正的士兵吗？没问题！但是你必须先经历刻苦的军训。东风吹，战鼓擂，咱们军训谁怕谁！注意了，所有关卡都必须一次性完成，否则你只能从头再来。<br>Commando Hero军训模拟器是一个非常具有挑战性的第三人称平台跳跃游戏。<br><br>在单人游戏中，你将在排行榜上和其他玩家竞速。多人游戏则会是一个非常欢乐的军训现场，你们将决出最终的军训标兵。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/9ac6ae0b89b0f4fe6af75e85b69a3bcb.poster.avif?t=1758112013\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/9ac6ae0b89b0f4fe6af75e85b69a3bcb.webm?t=1758112013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203990/extras/9ac6ae0b89b0f4fe6af75e85b69a3bcb.mp4?t=1758112013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你通过的速度越快越好！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></li><li>你必须要拥有敏捷的反应力<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></li><li>你每一关的排名将会在一次性通过所有障碍后获得！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></li><li>你懂的！在战争中，可没有“保存”的选项。</li></ul></h2>",
